Kulesi sithangami, athe azimisele ukuba i-ANCYL ibuyiselwe esimeni iphinde ikwazi ukusebenzela abantu abasha. “Kunezifunda nezifundazwe ezingakawaqinisekisi amagama amalungu e-ANCYL. Kodwa kukhona amagatsha angaphezu kuka-2 000 wona esekwenzile lokho, zikhona nezifundazwe eseziyilindele ingqungquthela. Ngakho-ke zonke izifundazwe zizonikezwa isikhathi sokuba zikwenze lokhu okufanele kokuletha amagama. Ingqungquthela yesi-26 ye-ANCYL izoqhubeka ngoMeyi 2020 e-University of Free State. Eminye imininingwane izothunyelwa maduze,” kusho isitatimende abasithumele ngemuva komhlangano. Amalungu aleli komiti kubalwa uMnuz Malusi Gigaba, Fikile Mbalula, Collen Maine, Dakota Legoete, noNkk Nomvula Mokonyane, bahlangana njalo ngamasonto ukuzohlelela le ngqungquthela.